					Full Description



		China Trends Holdings Limited is a Hong Kong-based investment holding company principally engaged in the trading of electronic technologies and related products. The Company operates through two business segments: the trading of electronic technology and related products segment and media operating segment. The Media Operating segment is involved in the provision of media and e-commerce platforms and media advertising services. The Company is also engaged in the provision of low-carbon products applications, including the development of low-carbon digital products solutions and applications. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in Hong Kong and the People’s Republic of China (the PRC).
» Full Overview of 8171.HK







