china trends holdings ltd (8171) Details


			China Trends Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in trading of electronic technology and related products, and LCD/LED products primarily in Hong Kong and Mainland China. The company develops low-carbon digital products solutions and applications; and provides media and e-commerce platforms, and media advertising services. China Trends Holdings Limited is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.
  			

